    "extras": [
      "An EasyCard or iPASS covers MRT, city buses, many TRA rides and YouBike unlocking across the route.",
      "THSR early-bird bookings can discount long hops like Taipei-Tainan or Kaohsiung-Taipei by up to roughly one-third.",
      "Taroko trail access can change after heavy rain or earthquake repairs, so re-check park notices the evening before your gorge day.",
      "Kuo-Kuang's airport 1819 route and Jiufen-bound 1062 route keep the north-Taiwan section simple without a car.",
      "Vegetarians should save Din Tai Fung, Fuhang Soy Milk, Jiufen Tea House, Du Hsiao Yueh side-dish options and Fo Guang Shan dining before landing."
